snippet.title: Zapper: One Wicked Cricket - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Uploaded for archiving purposes.

This trailer was played in the two level PC-Demo of Zapper: One Wicked Cricket. 

The game was released for PC, GameCube, PS2, XBOX and Game Boy Advance. It was developed by Blitz Games and published by Infogrames.
